# Frontend (SvelteKit)

## Stack

SvelteKit 2, Svelte 5, TypeScript strict, Vitest + Testing Library, static adapter. Supabase via `@supabase/supabase-js` and `getSupabaseBrowser()` in `$lib/supabaseClient.ts`.

## Layout

- `src/routes/` — pages and layouts (`+page.svelte`, `+page.ts`, `+layout.ts`)
- `src/lib/` — components, domain logic, shared styles (`styles/ui.css`)
- Specs next to features: `src/lib/**/*.spec.ts`

## Patterns

- Env: `import.meta.env.SUPABASE_URL` / `SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY` only — never service-role keys
- Supabase writes go through RPCs defined in migrations when RLS requires it (e.g. `create_vote_with_options`)
- Voting method values: `$lib/votingMethods.ts`
- UI strings and education copy: `$lib/education/`

## Verify

```bash
make frontend-test      # vitest
make frontend-check     # svelte-check + eslint + vitest
```

Domain rules for votes/ballots: **`product-spec.md`**.
